* Page Checks
** URL
*** Address
*** Consistent NAP

** Local SEO
*** Name, Address, Phone (NAP)
**** Consistent with Business Registration
**** Consistent with Google Maps
*** Claim on Google Maps
*** Directories (yelp, Urbanspoon etc.)
*** Reviews and Citations
**** Quality
**** Quantity (typ. > 100)
*** Inbound links
*** Google Photos

** Structure
*** Unique url, page title, description, H1
*** Page title (clear & simple with keywords)
*** H1 (short, clear, concise, active voice, describe page content)
*** Description
*** Content Heirarchy (H2, H3 etc.)
*** Paragraphs vs. Bullets

** Images

** Content
*** No Keyword Stuffing
*** No Cloaking (i.e. Doorway) Pages
*** No Hidden text
*** Content Duplication
*** Repetitive anchor text
*** A Page with single search objective

** General Compatibility
*** Mobile friendliness
*** Page loading  time
*** Robots.txt
*** XML Sitemaps


** Links
*** Practical (context) outbound links
*** Inbound links

** Sanity Checks
*** Hidden Pages
*** Stuffing words into alt text

